<div class='layout'><p>A rather gentle womans voice said,……dame is Dors Venabili……I have come to……Dr. Hari Seldon."</p><p>一个颇为温柔的女声答道：“我名叫铎丝·凡纳比里，我来找哈里·谢顿博士。”</p></div>
<div class='layout'><p>Even as that……said, a woman……standing just in front of……door, without that door ever having been opened.</p><p>话还未说完，一名女子已经站在门边，此时房门绝对尚未打开。</p></div>
