<div class='layout'><p>He peered……cautiously,……only……woman, then opened……door sufficiently to allow……to enter. He immediately closed……locked……door behind her. </p><p>他小心翼翼地向外窥探，结果仅仅见到那名女子，于是将房门再拉开一点，刚好足够让她进来。然后，他立刻将房门关上并锁好。</p></div>
