<div class='layout'><p>"Do I pass inspection?"……asked. (She seemed to have Hummins trick of guessing……thoughts, Seldon thought, or perhaps he himself lacked……trick of hiding them.)</p><p>“我通过检查了吗？”她问道。（谢顿心想，她似乎和夫铭一样，也有本事猜中自己的心思，但也或许是他自己没有隐藏心思的本事。）</p></div>
