<div class='layout'><p>"Youll find I am not."</p><p>“你会发现其实不然。”</p></div>
<div class='layout'><p>"Well,……try to be as little trouble as possible. Could……please repeat your name?"</p><p>“好吧，我会尽量不惹麻烦。可否请你再讲一遍你的名字？”</p></div>
